channel.title: Me inside of runescape
channel.description: So I decided to take my photo shopping to the next level by my standards and decided to make myself cast a vengeance this is my 3rd picture that I ever did in Photoshop. This photo required 3 different photos, one of me in the stance, one of me casting a vengeance and one of me being in the wild [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/2MztPea.jpg[/img]

item.title: Me inside of runescape
item.dc:creator: @stCky stCky
item.description:
@stCky wrote:

Heh, funny idea and you gave it a good shot. Obviously a couple of minor details already mentioned (minimap dot etc) would help but other than that you demonstrate your knowledge of a new tool and that’s what it’s all about (Y)

People think it’s weird or faggy 'cause you’re shopping yourself into runescape but hey, some people on this forum like ponies so you can’t be that bad.

Challenge: Add a dot to the minimap and chuck some armour or weapons on yourself for v2
